# Loredeck-builder .skill bundle: everything under these dirs is generated by
# sync-from-repo.mjs from the real sources (.claude/skills/loredeck-builder,
# tools/loredeck, docs/loredecks, content/loredecks/hp-core, src/loredecks,
# src/lorecards) and then zipped by build-skill-file.mjs. None of it is
# hand-edited, so none of it is committed -- run sync-from-repo.mjs to
# regenerate locally. See plugins/loredeck-builder/README.md.
plugins/loredeck-builder/skills/
plugins/loredeck-builder/cli/
plugins/loredeck-builder/docs/
plugins/loredeck-builder/reference-decks/
plugins/loredeck-builder/dist/

